creator: Lifepoint Informatics
descriptionHtml:
PDL's PDLConnect delivers real-time access to laboratory results on your Android device. With a built in notification system, providers will receive critical value alerts on the go. Conveniently configurable filters allow providers to personalize screen information to their own preference.

PDLConnect’s Key Features:
- Secure log-in
- Critical Value Alerts
- Inbox presentation of lab results, & AP reports
- Alternative PDF report view with AirPrint functionality
- Highlighted identification of abnormal results
- Historical Test Search
- Dynamic inbox for filtering results
descriptionShort: Real-time access to Laboratory, Pathology and Diagnostic Imaging test results.
